{"tid":575510,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"［迫害爺爺］下季英超第四可直入歐聯分組賽","createTime":"2018-02-28T08:47:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-28T10:05:12.000Z","uid":4661,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7870708948b2c1dd88a13708f20185fdf8aaa80f","tid":575510,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T08:47:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/bmCYInJc2M8/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FbmCYInJc2M8%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=0bd5e4b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據歐洲足協規定，英超頭三位才可直入歐聯分組賽，而第四位就要打附加賽，情況有如今年的利物浦。歐洲足協今日正式發佈新規，指自18/19球季開始，歐洲四大聯賽英超、西甲、德甲以及意甲的前四球會可直入分組賽。<br />\n<br />\n歐洲足協早在2016年已預告會在18/19球季實施新規，而下賽季將有26支球隊直入歐聯分組賽，當中包括四大聯賽的16支頭四球隊、衛冕歐聯以及歐霸冠軍、法甲以及俄超頭二以及比利時、烏克蘭、土耳其、葡萄牙的聯賽冠軍。至於其餘6隊就是來自其他聯賽，他們都要打附加賽。<br />\n<br />\n另開波時間都會有改變，由慣常的20:45CET(歐洲中部時間)改成了18:55CET或21:00CET，但這對香港球迷影響不大，因為無論如何都要捱夜睇波。而歐洲足協主席施費連（Aleksander Ceferin）亦表示，下屆歐聯不會應用VAR（視像裁判）。"},{"pid":"c8f7caf1b908319b38f739d353256038e75e6620","tid":575510,"uid":22364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T08:53:30.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n早呢2粒鐘差好遠喎<br />\n變左香港時間1點幾開"},{"pid":"00daaeeb41a87cb9dcdc93d61476862f65f80e70","tid":575510,"uid":693,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T08:58:43.000Z","msg":"2點開波姐係好似去俄羅斯打早場咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好難訓一陣起身睇<br />\n<br />\n3點9可以訓一陣起身睇"},{"pid":"fc4dff17e7e8a9bf6403bc534b20fe8144d696d0","tid":575510,"uid":158791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T08:59:54.000Z","msg":"我廠不屑踢歐聯<br />\n劍指歐霸"},{"pid":"ad9def19f57b0697a91d8b0c02baf05bd9080c0e","tid":575510,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T09:00:41.000Z","msg":"學英超有香港時間12點場 10點場 最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94f0db5890ba40563d524e3efd5d3529554967ca","tid":575510,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T09:00:56.000Z","msg":"歐霸冠軍都得啦屌"},{"pid":"9aade54c43a902973dba391365862b09cd6c62b6","tid":575510,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T09:03:36.000Z","msg":"無得踢附加賽搵少場錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b231cfd61a9f276e8581a7c8b2a41eb35a01347","tid":575510,"uid":59966,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ad9def19f57b0697a91d8b0c02baf05bd9080c0e","tid":575510,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T09:00:41.000Z","msg":"學英超有香港時間12點場 10點場 最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T09:05:50.000Z","msg":"歐聯週中打冇可能有呢啲時間啦"},{"pid":"4bf39d0919fee7f040673358f78970c92578e4d4","tid":575510,"uid":55,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T09:07:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"48de1354d52445b85e2fb9c83ae6accbad695163","tid":575510,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T09:08:39.000Z","msg":"1點睇到3點 8點起身 not bad"},{"pid":"fa89cc6d99f2f23d371c203ab956a1615cecfda5","tid":575510,"uid":54524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T09:11:09.000Z","msg":"荷甲冠軍都要打附加賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2abc933800194632b148eb206bc6f5a829b0ae99","tid":575510,"uid":6242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48de1354d52445b85e2fb9c83ae6accbad695163","tid":575510,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T09:08:39.000Z","msg":"1點睇到3點 8點起身 not bad"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T09:27:16.000Z","msg":"香港快七個鐘喎<br />\n早場都兩點"},{"pid":"b2d5d7a79a902114b90929fdadc6ab87e1847a34","tid":575510,"uid":36324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00daaeeb41a87cb9dcdc93d61476862f65f80e70","tid":575510,"uid":693,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T08:58:4